WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.333
Now imagine a hill made of loss.

00:00:02.333 --> 00:00:04.667
High where we are very wrong, low

00:00:04.667 --> 00:00:06.000
where we are close.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Feel the ground.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:08.333
Which way tilts downward?

00:00:08.333 --> 00:00:10.000
That direction is the slope.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.333
So, the slope points the way toward

00:00:12.333 --> 00:00:13.000
less loss.
